00:03:44.950 --> 00:03:48.140
So we came out here to the
outskirts of Tynda and we

00:03:48.140 --> 00:03:49.240
found the North Korean

00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:51.680
Administration Camp Number Two.

00:03:51.680 --> 00:03:53.310
Surprise, surprise, they
won't let us in.

00:03:53.310 --> 00:03:56.330
But we're going to go deeper
into the interior to find the

00:03:56.330 --> 00:03:58.860
actual work camps and
see if we can talk

00:03:58.860 --> 00:04:00.110
to some of the dudes.

00:04:03.440 --> 00:04:07.040
So we're leaving on a one-car
train to go to the north

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:08.060
Korean camps.

00:04:08.060 --> 00:04:09.950
It's a one-car train.

00:04:09.950 --> 00:04:11.680
